---
title: Korean Style Honey Beef Noodles with Pepper, Lime and Peanuts
description: Ready in less than 25 minutes, these Speedy Korean Style Honey Beef Noodles combine spicy-sweet gochujang with honey to make a deliciously sticky sauce to coat the noodles and beef. Finish with lime juice and sprinkle with peanuts for full-on flavour.
